location.fullValue: The Fairview I Plan, Woodland Creek - 2 Homes Remaining!

data.description: Beautifully maintained and move-in ready with a prime location on Hole #2 in Stone River Estates.  The home is one story, has an open floor plan with three bedrooms and three full bathrooms.  All three bedrooms are split for privacy.  One of the secondary bedrooms has an en suite bathroom with a walk-in shower.  There is an office with French doors upon entering the home and a separate dining room as well as an eat-in kitchen.  You will love the beautiful wood floors, a neutral color scheme, and quartz countertops.  Whether a golfer or not, Stone River offers a unique yet peaceful golf course lifestyle and sunset views of the golf course on the covered patio are top notch!
